6
00:00:27,634 --> 00:00:29,406
<font color="yellow">I didn't do it!</font>

7
00:00:33,031 --> 00:00:35,898
<font color="yellow">We're going to confiscate this as evidence.</font>

8
00:00:38,696 --> 00:00:41,775
<font color="yellow">Please follow us to the audit
room for further investigation.</font>

9
00:00:42,774 --> 00:00:43,774
<font color="yellow">I'll take her.</font>

10
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:49,452
<font color="yellow">Fine. Please bring her to the audit room.</font>

11
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,000
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

12
00:01:08,172 --> 00:01:09,305
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

13
00:01:10,335 --> 00:01:12,664
<font color="yellow">Cash was found in Kim Mi-poong's drawer?</font>

14
00:01:13,492 --> 00:01:14,492
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

15
00:01:15,711 --> 00:01:16,846
<font color="yellow">$300,000 was found.</font>

16
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:21,625
<font color="yellow">We are currently investigating her past and
the process of the leakage of information.</font>

17
00:01:21,805 --> 00:01:26,613
<font color="yellow">However, she keeps denying it,
so it'll take some time.</font>

18
00:01:26,889 --> 00:01:30,133
<font color="yellow">Leaking company information is unacceptable.</font>

19
00:01:30,883 --> 00:01:34,449
<font color="yellow">Make sure you thoroughly investigate this
to find out how the design was disclosed.</font>

20
00:01:34,992 --> 00:01:35,992
<font color="yellow">Yes, I will.</font>

21
00:01:44,922 --> 00:01:46,250
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee Jang-go?</font>

22
00:01:48,094 --> 00:01:49,494
<font color="yellow">What brings you here?</font>

23
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:54,093
<font color="yellow">Oh, he works as a lawyer in
Winner Group's legal investigation team.</font>

24
00:01:55,156 --> 00:01:56,672
<font color="yellow">Oh, really?</font>

25
00:01:57,914 --> 00:01:58,914
<font color="yellow">Since when?</font>

26
00:01:59,149 --> 00:02:00,149
<font color="yellow">Just recently.</font>

27
00:02:03,406 --> 00:02:05,570
<font color="yellow">- Hello.
- Hi.</font>

28
00:02:08,336 --> 00:02:11,476
<font color="yellow">But he's Kim Mi-poong's husband.</font>

29
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,827
<font color="yellow">Will he be part of this investigation?</font>

30
00:02:13,852 --> 00:02:17,481
<font color="yellow">Of course not. As the rules state, families
cannot be involved in the investigations.</font>

31
00:02:17,899 --> 00:02:19,709
<font color="yellow">Mr. Han. Ms. Park.</font>

32
00:02:20,344 --> 00:02:24,426
<font color="yellow">I am Kim Mi-poong's husband, but I am
also part of the investigation team.</font>

33
00:02:24,633 --> 00:02:26,945
<font color="yellow">I have the confidence to be
as objective as possible.</font>

34
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,961
<font color="yellow">Please let me be a part of it.</font>

35
00:02:28,986 --> 00:02:32,055
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee, please abide by the rules.</font>

36
00:02:32,656 --> 00:02:35,264
<font color="yellow">You can't help but be subjective
to your family members.</font>

37
00:02:37,071 --> 00:02:40,739
<font color="yellow">Mr. Han, make sure Mr. Lee
can't be part of this investigation.</font>

38
00:02:41,641 --> 00:02:42,641
<font color="yellow">Yes, ma'am.</font>

39
00:02:50,641 --> 00:02:51,641
<font color="yellow">Sir.</font>

40
00:02:52,930 --> 00:02:55,968
<font color="yellow">Please allow me to at least
speak to Kim Mi-poong.</font>

41
00:02:57,008 --> 00:02:58,008
<font color="yellow">Mr. Lee.</font>

42
00:02:58,033 --> 00:02:59,100
<font color="yellow">I'm begging you.</font>

43
00:03:10,773 --> 00:03:14,309
<font color="yellow">How can Mi-poong's husband be
working in our investigation team?</font>

44
00:03:15,547 --> 00:03:20,480
<font color="yellow">However, no matter what he does,
she won't be able to get out of this one.</font>

45
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,484
<font color="yellow">I don't know what happened.</font>

46
00:03:27,016 --> 00:03:30,776
<font color="yellow">I don't know how the apparels I designed were</font>

47
00:03:30,801 --> 00:03:34,560
<font color="yellow">released as the products
of our rival company.</font>

48
00:03:35,444 --> 00:03:39,545
<font color="yellow">I don't know why such a large amount
of money was in my drawer either.</font>

49
00:03:43,155 --> 00:03:44,688
<font color="yellow">What happens to me now?</font>

50
00:03:45,569 --> 00:03:47,545
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong. Kim Mi-poong.</font>

51
00:03:49,452 --> 00:03:51,569
<font color="yellow">Look into my eyes. Focus here.</font>

52
00:03:52,475 --> 00:03:54,278
<font color="yellow">You can't become weak-hearted.</font>

53
00:03:54,749 --> 00:03:56,051
<font color="yellow">Get your head together, got it?</font>

54
00:03:59,811 --> 00:04:01,673
<font color="yellow">Did anyone approach you lately?</font>

55
00:04:02,983 --> 00:04:06,299
<font color="yellow">Did anyone ask you to hand over the design?</font>

56
00:04:07,163 --> 00:04:08,163
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

57
00:04:09,483 --> 00:04:11,216
<font color="yellow">I never saw or met anyone.</font>

58
00:04:13,210 --> 00:04:14,210
<font color="yellow">Really?</font>

59
00:04:15,616 --> 00:04:17,719
<font color="yellow">Then when was the last time
you opened that drawer?</font>

60
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,639
<font color="yellow">Yesterday.</font>

61
00:04:19,897 --> 00:04:22,097
<font color="yellow">There wasn't any money in it yesterday.</font>

62
00:04:23,452 --> 00:04:24,452
<font color="yellow">Are you sure?</font>

63
00:04:24,733 --> 00:04:25,733
<font color="yellow">I'm sure.</font>

64
00:04:28,272 --> 00:04:30,672
<font color="yellow">That means this happened last night.</font>

65
00:04:31,514 --> 00:04:33,506
<font color="yellow">I don't know why this happened to me.</font>

66
00:04:35,053 --> 00:04:37,289
<font color="yellow">I feel like my heart is going to burst.</font>

67
00:04:38,014 --> 00:04:41,784
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, I'm going to find out
who did this to you.</font>

68
00:04:43,262 --> 00:04:45,449
<font color="yellow">You didn't do this,
so the truth will be revealed.</font>

69
00:04:46,613 --> 00:04:47,613
<font color="yellow">So don't worry.</font>

70
00:04:48,295 --> 00:04:50,709
<font color="yellow">But that's not what's important right now.</font>

71
00:04:51,606 --> 00:04:54,781
<font color="yellow">I don't care what happens to me,
but the apparels</font>

72
00:04:54,805 --> 00:04:57,725
<font color="yellow">I made were supposed
to be released next week.</font>

73
00:04:58,512 --> 00:05:01,413
<font color="yellow">But the apparels that were made
in the factory are useless now.</font>

74
00:05:02,028 --> 00:05:03,028
<font color="yellow">What do I do?</font>

75
00:05:05,317 --> 00:05:06,707
<font color="yellow">What do I do?</font>

76
00:05:19,434 --> 00:05:20,701
<font color="yellow">Grandma, this, too.</font>

77
00:05:21,449 --> 00:05:22,558
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear.</font>

78
00:05:22,948 --> 00:05:25,151
<font color="yellow">We almost forgot the fly swatter.</font>

79
00:05:25,176 --> 00:05:27,267
<font color="yellow">Yes, we almost left this
important thing behind.</font>

80
00:05:28,223 --> 00:05:30,277
<font color="yellow">Good job, Yoo-sung.</font>

81
00:05:36,387 --> 00:05:41,589
<font color="yellow">- It seems like you're almost done packing.
- Yes, I'm almost done.</font>

82
00:05:42,238 --> 00:05:46,940
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear. I couldn't even help
you out. You worked hard.</font>

83
00:05:46,965 --> 00:05:49,898
<font color="yellow">No, it's fine. I don't have a lot of things.</font>

84
00:05:50,403 --> 00:05:53,171
<font color="yellow">Until a few days ago,
we had a party together.</font>

85
00:05:53,418 --> 00:05:55,730
<font color="yellow">I was happy that we were
finally getting along.</font>

86
00:05:56,769 --> 00:06:00,470
<font color="yellow">You're moving away out of the blue.</font>

87
00:06:01,926 --> 00:06:05,082
<font color="yellow">I feel so upset and guilty.</font>

88
00:06:06,465 --> 00:06:10,951
<font color="yellow">No ma'am. I should be the sorry one.
Thank you for everything.</font>

89
00:06:11,918 --> 00:06:14,248
<font color="yellow">Don't worry about Mi-poong.</font>

90
00:06:14,559 --> 00:06:18,066
<font color="yellow">I'll treat her like she's
my own granddaughter.</font>

91
00:06:20,129 --> 00:06:22,175
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

92
00:06:24,324 --> 00:06:28,199
<font color="yellow">Oh, my handsome Yoo-sung.</font>

93
00:06:28,597 --> 00:06:32,418
<font color="yellow">I'm going to miss you
so much. What will I do?</font>

94
00:06:32,910 --> 00:06:36,965
<font color="yellow">Your aunt lives here,
so come visit her often.</font>

95
00:06:37,184 --> 00:06:38,465
<font color="yellow">Yes, grandma.</font>

96
00:06:39,598 --> 00:06:45,395
<font color="yellow">Take this and buy something yummy.</font>

97
00:06:46,379 --> 00:06:48,480
<font color="yellow">Yes, grandma. Thank you.</font>

98
00:06:50,535 --> 00:06:52,595
<font color="yellow">You're so precious.</font>

99
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,879
<font color="yellow">- Should we take these out?
- Yes, please.</font>

100
00:07:06,457 --> 00:07:08,790
<font color="yellow">Mom, what's wrong? Did someone die?</font>

101
00:07:09,012 --> 00:07:11,261
<font color="yellow">Don't say such nonsense!</font>

102
00:07:12,387 --> 00:07:15,704
<font color="yellow">Ms. Joo is really moving away.</font>

103
00:07:16,168 --> 00:07:18,995
<font color="yellow">- They're moving out their things right now.
- Really? Right now?</font>

104
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:22,770
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil,</font>

105
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:27,933
<font color="yellow">I don't think this is right.</font>

106
00:07:28,270 --> 00:07:29,403
<font color="yellow">What's not right?</font>

107
00:07:30,035 --> 00:07:34,027
<font color="yellow">About Ms. Joo. I feel terrible about this.</font>

108
00:07:34,238 --> 00:07:37,682
<font color="yellow">Aside from everything else,
you shouldn't send her away like</font>

109
00:07:37,707 --> 00:07:41,150
<font color="yellow">you're kicking her out of here.
Don't you think that's wrong?</font>

110
00:07:41,981 --> 00:07:46,389
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil, how about we stop
them from moving right now?</font>

111
00:07:47,231 --> 00:07:50,347
<font color="yellow">Mother, why are you saying this now?</font>

112
00:07:51,183 --> 00:07:54,545
<font color="yellow">I don't know how you feel, but
I feel like a load is off my mind.</font>

113
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:58,090
<font color="yellow">Now that they're finally moving out,
I feel like my toothache is gone.</font>

114
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,777
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness.</font>

115
00:08:00,192 --> 00:08:03,066
<font color="yellow">How could you be so cruel?</font>

116
00:08:04,473 --> 00:08:06,957
<font color="yellow">The three of them came down
from North Korea together.</font>

117
00:08:06,982 --> 00:08:09,194
<font color="yellow">Do you think it's right that
you tear them apart?</font>

118
00:08:09,351 --> 00:08:11,863
<font color="yellow">Especially in this frigid weather?</font>

119
00:08:12,848 --> 00:08:16,416
<font color="yellow">Mother, we didn't tear their family apart.</font>

120
00:08:16,723 --> 00:08:21,183
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong left her family behind
to get married to Jang-go.</font>

121
00:08:21,723 --> 00:08:25,409
<font color="yellow">And they lived for free
in that house until now.</font>

122
00:08:26,051 --> 00:08:30,285
<font color="yellow">We did as much as we could,
so we don't have to feel terrible at all.</font>

123
00:08:32,301 --> 00:08:35,373
<font color="yellow">And even if we beg that woman to stay, do you</font>

124
00:08:35,398 --> 00:08:38,403
<font color="yellow">think she'll be able to out of embarrassment?</font>

125
00:08:39,193 --> 00:08:41,669
<font color="yellow">If she has a conscience,
she wouldn't be able to live here.</font>

126
00:08:41,967 --> 00:08:43,302
<font color="yellow">My goodness.</font>

127
00:08:43,327 --> 00:08:46,638
<font color="yellow">No matter how much she needed a man.
No matter how much there was no man around.</font>

128
00:08:46,717 --> 00:08:50,397
<font color="yellow">Because I'm so ashamed
of what she did, I can't even</font>

129
00:08:50,422 --> 00:08:54,101
<font color="yellow">go out and I'm stuck here
preparing the bean sprouts.</font>

130
00:08:54,521 --> 00:09:00,310
<font color="yellow">Goodness, Geum-sil.
Ms. Joo said that isn't true.</font>

131
00:09:00,513 --> 00:09:04,176
<font color="yellow">It's not that big of a deal to like someone.</font>

132
00:09:04,201 --> 00:09:06,490
<font color="yellow">If she did like him, she would've said so.</font>

133
00:09:06,709 --> 00:09:09,232
<font color="yellow">She said it isn't true because it isn't true.</font>

134
00:09:09,778 --> 00:09:16,843
<font color="yellow">And I don't think she's the type
to steal another woman's man.</font>

135
00:09:17,178 --> 00:09:19,154
<font color="yellow">So let's believe her.</font>

136
00:09:19,529 --> 00:09:21,271
<font color="yellow">You go ahead and believe her.</font>

137
00:09:21,592 --> 00:09:24,655
<font color="yellow">I don't want to see that woman ever again.</font>

138
00:09:26,576 --> 00:09:29,737
<font color="yellow">How dare you call
your in-law "that woman!"</font>

139
00:09:29,762 --> 00:09:32,669
<font color="yellow">Where did you learn your
manners from? How ignorant!</font>

140
00:09:33,435 --> 00:09:35,775
<font color="yellow">Stop it. You lost.</font>

141
00:09:38,185 --> 00:09:39,185
<font color="yellow">I'm back.</font>

142
00:09:42,708 --> 00:09:45,505
<font color="yellow">Aunt. Grandma. It seems like
Yoo-sung's family is moving away.</font>

143
00:09:45,845 --> 00:09:47,490
<font color="yellow">There's a moving truck outside.</font>

144
00:09:55,154 --> 00:09:57,221
<font color="yellow">- Is this the last one?
- Yes.</font>

145
00:10:01,975 --> 00:10:04,318
<font color="yellow">Oh, it's that ring.</font>

146
00:10:05,256 --> 00:10:06,981
<font color="yellow">But why is this here?</font>

147
00:10:15,170 --> 00:10:18,412
<font color="yellow">The ring was here.</font>

148
00:10:20,209 --> 00:10:21,974
<font color="yellow">How did this happen?</font>

149
00:10:22,725 --> 00:10:24,792
<font color="yellow">I thought I had lost this ring.</font>

150
00:10:25,287 --> 00:10:27,794
<font color="yellow">I guess it was under
the wardrobe all this time.</font>

151
00:10:28,475 --> 00:10:30,318
<font color="yellow">Is that your ring?</font>

152
00:10:30,881 --> 00:10:36,206
<font color="yellow">Yes, this is my ring.
I was so upset when I had lost it.</font>

153
00:10:38,068 --> 00:10:40,830
<font color="yellow">Because we're moving,
I was able to find this ring.</font>

154
00:10:42,365 --> 00:10:46,863
<font color="yellow">But I think I saw a ring like this before.</font>

155
00:10:46,888 --> 00:10:50,207
<font color="yellow">Of course you did because I was wearing it.</font>

156
00:10:51,482 --> 00:10:55,089
<font color="yellow">You did something great today.</font>

157
00:10:55,467 --> 00:10:57,232
<font color="yellow">You found this precious ring for me.</font>

158
00:10:59,303 --> 00:11:00,970
<font color="yellow">We're done. Should we go?</font>

159
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,458
<font color="yellow">- Yes.
- Okay.</font>

160
00:11:04,115 --> 00:11:05,382
<font color="yellow">Let's go, Yoo-sung.</font>

161
00:11:13,725 --> 00:11:16,099
<font color="yellow">Thank you for everything. Good-bye.</font>

162
00:11:16,334 --> 00:11:20,317
<font color="yellow">- Hurry and get in the car. The driver is waiting.
- Okay.</font>

163
00:11:21,428 --> 00:11:23,115
<font color="yellow">- Go safely.
- Bye, Yoo-sung.</font>

164
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:25,387
<font color="yellow">- Bye.
- Bye.</font>

165
00:11:37,373 --> 00:11:40,779
<font color="yellow">You're right. I don't feel right
since they're leaving like this.</font>

166
00:11:41,396 --> 00:11:45,551
<font color="yellow">I know. Mi-poong will feel really sad when
she comes home and sees the empty house.</font>

167
00:11:45,928 --> 00:11:48,612
<font color="yellow">People feel sad even when
a dog runs away from home.</font>

168
00:11:49,591 --> 00:11:51,732
<font color="yellow">But she doesn't even
come out to say good-bye?</font>

169
00:11:51,757 --> 00:11:53,710
<font color="yellow">Just ignore it.</font>

170
00:11:54,037 --> 00:11:56,021
<font color="yellow">You're going to make it noisy.
I'm going to work.</font>

171
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,810
<font color="yellow">- Me, too, grandma.
- Let's go.</font>

172
00:12:03,568 --> 00:12:07,537
<font color="yellow">What will she do with
little Yoo-sung on her own?</font>

173
00:12:13,615 --> 00:12:17,172
<font color="yellow">Grandma, are you happy
that you found the ring?</font>

174
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,896
<font color="yellow">Of course I am.</font>

175
00:12:20,193 --> 00:12:22,767
<font color="yellow">This is the ring that
your grandfather gave</font>

176
00:12:22,792 --> 00:12:25,312
<font color="yellow">your grandmother when
they separated from each other.</font>

177
00:12:26,170 --> 00:12:29,821
<font color="yellow">I see. It really is a precious ring.</font>

178
00:12:31,818 --> 00:12:35,179
<font color="yellow">I should call your aunt and let her know.</font>

179
00:12:35,607 --> 00:12:37,140
<font color="yellow">She'll be so surprised.</font>

180
00:12:37,943 --> 00:12:41,395
<font color="yellow">The person you are trying
to reach is unavailable.</font>

181
00:12:41,420 --> 00:12:43,669
<font color="yellow">Maybe she's busy.
She's not answering her phone.</font>

182
00:12:46,661 --> 00:12:48,482
<font color="yellow">It's the same one.</font>

183
00:12:49,107 --> 00:12:51,545
<font color="yellow">What did you say?</font>

184
00:12:52,115 --> 00:12:53,827
<font color="yellow">It's nothing.</font>

185
00:12:55,357 --> 00:12:56,357
<font color="yellow">Yoo-sung.</font>

186
00:12:58,864 --> 00:13:03,487
<font color="yellow">From now on, only you
and I will be living together.</font>

187
00:13:03,878 --> 00:13:10,335
<font color="yellow">Now that we found your grandfather's ring,
let's be strong and live well.</font>

188
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:11,870
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

189
00:13:25,136 --> 00:13:26,269
<font color="yellow">Ms. Kim Mi-poong.</font>

190
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:28,362
<font color="yellow">(Accident Report)</font>

191
00:13:28,387 --> 00:13:32,590
<font color="yellow">Please write down everything in order that
has happened from the design planning</font>

192
00:13:32,615 --> 00:13:36,466
<font color="yellow">of the leaked sportswear to the
situation that has happened today.</font>

193
00:13:37,035 --> 00:13:39,558
<font color="yellow">Make sure you write down all
the people you have met, the time</font>

194
00:13:39,583 --> 00:13:42,145
<font color="yellow">you met them, the locations,
and the topic of the conversations.</font>

195
00:13:42,957 --> 00:13:43,957
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

196
00:14:19,543 --> 00:14:20,543
<font color="yellow">Welcome!</font>

197
00:14:21,137 --> 00:14:24,144
<font color="yellow">Is the boss here?</font>

198
