<font color="yellow">Tell me as Kim Mi-poong's husband.</font>

402
00:28:34,374 --> 00:28:37,447
<font color="yellow">I had to beg the chairman in
order not to demand</font>

403
00:28:37,472 --> 00:28:40,484
<font color="yellow">a compensation for the
great loss from Kim Mi-poong.</font>

404
00:28:41,718 --> 00:28:43,185
<font color="yellow">So you should end this now.</font>

405
00:28:48,874 --> 00:28:49,874
<font color="yellow">One more thing.</font>

406
00:28:51,906 --> 00:28:55,039
<font color="yellow">You have been hired to
work for Winner's Group.</font>

407
00:28:56,148 --> 00:28:59,397
<font color="yellow">Before you defend your family,
you should consider the company first.</font>

408
00:29:00,647 --> 00:29:02,733
<font color="yellow">If you don't like that, you should leave.</font>

409
00:29:36,960 --> 00:29:37,976
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong!</font>

410
00:29:38,999 --> 00:29:39,999
<font color="yellow">Jang-go!</font>

411
00:29:43,867 --> 00:29:45,910
<font color="yellow">Why didn't you answer your phone?</font>

412
00:29:46,217 --> 00:29:48,463
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. I didn't know
I had run out of battery.</font>

413
00:29:52,210 --> 00:29:55,203
<font color="yellow">You're frozen. You should have
gone in somewhere. It's cold.</font>

414
00:29:56,085 --> 00:30:01,018
<font color="yellow">I didn't want to take that box and
go inside a place with a lot of people.</font>

415
00:30:02,851 --> 00:30:03,851
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry.</font>

416
00:30:05,046 --> 00:30:11,450
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, I thought I had lived a good
life without being mean to anybody.</font>

417
00:30:12,328 --> 00:30:14,778
<font color="yellow">I have no idea why this is happening to me.</font>

418
00:30:16,335 --> 00:30:19,245
<font color="yellow">If I had really done something wrong,</font>

419
00:30:19,270 --> 00:30:22,179
<font color="yellow">I would gladly be punished,
but this is really unfair!</font>

420
00:30:23,359 --> 00:30:25,475
<font color="yellow">I'm so shocked that
my heart is beating fast.</font>

421
00:30:26,702 --> 00:30:31,427
<font color="yellow">I'll return you to your place. I'll make
sure to reveal that it's not your fault.</font>

422
00:30:32,617 --> 00:30:33,617
<font color="yellow">I promise.</font>

423
00:30:38,687 --> 00:30:41,686
<font color="yellow">But what do I tell the family?</font>

424
00:30:42,491 --> 00:30:44,850
<font color="yellow">Mother will say something if she finds out.</font>

425
00:30:45,578 --> 00:30:47,311
<font color="yellow">And what do I tell my mom?</font>

426
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:50,999
<font color="yellow">My mom will be so upset
if she finds out I was fired.</font>

427
00:30:55,397 --> 00:30:57,593
<font color="yellow">For now, let's not tell anyone.</font>

428
00:31:00,156 --> 00:31:02,031
<font color="yellow">I'll do something about this in the meantime.</font>

429
00:31:03,851 --> 00:31:05,651
<font color="yellow">Then what do I do tomorrow?</font>

430
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:08,359
<font color="yellow">Tomorrow...</font>

431
00:31:10,538 --> 00:31:12,890
<font color="yellow">Just leave the house with me
as if you're going to work.</font>

432
00:31:13,350 --> 00:31:17,550
<font color="yellow">You can go to the movies,
bookstore, and museum.</font>

433
00:31:18,226 --> 00:31:20,159
<font color="yellow">You can have some alone time.</font>

434
00:31:20,184 --> 00:31:22,184
<font color="yellow">Thinking about it,
it sounds like a good idea.</font>

435
00:31:25,421 --> 00:31:26,421
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

436
00:31:27,148 --> 00:31:28,148
<font color="yellow">No problem.</font>

437
00:31:29,085 --> 00:31:31,475
<font color="yellow">We're a married couple.
And what are married couples?</font>

438
00:31:31,812 --> 00:31:33,012
<font color="yellow">One body and soul.</font>

439
00:31:34,124 --> 00:31:35,413
<font color="yellow">You're so smart.</font>

440
00:31:36,718 --> 00:31:38,116
<font color="yellow">Let's go now.</font>

441
00:31:38,531 --> 00:31:39,531
<font color="yellow">Go where?</font>

442
00:31:39,556 --> 00:31:41,968
<font color="yellow">Look at you. Wake up.</font>

443
00:31:42,585 --> 00:31:46,445
<font color="yellow">- Aren't you going to your mother's new home?
- That's right! She moved today!</font>

444
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:49,373
<font color="yellow">I wasn't in my right mind.</font>

445
00:31:49,445 --> 00:31:50,965
<font color="yellow">Are you in your right mind now?</font>

446
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:55,381
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, you need to come
to your senses. Okay?</font>

447
00:31:55,781 --> 00:31:56,781
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

448
00:32:15,929 --> 00:32:16,929
<font color="yellow">It's cold.</font>

449
00:32:16,954 --> 00:32:19,287
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, can you tell that I cried?</font>

450
00:32:20,078 --> 00:32:21,817
<font color="yellow">No. You look pretty.</font>

451
00:32:22,179 --> 00:32:23,179
<font color="yellow">Are you sure?</font>

452
00:32:23,734 --> 00:32:27,382
<font color="yellow">My mom can always tell whenever I cried.</font>

453
00:32:27,992 --> 00:32:29,554
<font color="yellow">I can't get caught.</font>

454
00:32:30,828 --> 00:32:33,155
<font color="yellow">Do you think it'll be okay
if I smile like this?</font>

455
00:32:33,921 --> 00:32:34,921
<font color="yellow">Yes.</font>

456
00:32:35,303 --> 00:32:36,303
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

457
00:32:36,921 --> 00:32:37,921
<font color="yellow">Mom!</font>

458
00:32:41,624 --> 00:32:43,146
<font color="yellow">Mom! Yoo-sung!</font>

459
00:32:43,172 --> 00:32:45,639
<font color="yellow">Mother! Yoo-sung, I bought pork feet!</font>

460
00:32:45,664 --> 00:32:49,015
<font color="yellow">- Aunt! Uncle!
- Welcome! It's cold outside, isn't it?</font>

461
00:32:49,187 --> 00:32:50,454
<font color="yellow">- Sit here.
- Okay.</font>

462
00:32:52,796 --> 00:32:53,796
<font color="yellow">It's cold.</font>

463
00:33:00,460 --> 00:33:03,810
<font color="yellow">Mother, I'll move you to a bigger,
better house in the future.</font>

464
00:33:04,859 --> 00:33:09,215
<font color="yellow">Thank you. This house is
enough for Yoo-sung and me.</font>

465
00:33:09,812 --> 00:33:11,604
<font color="yellow">The house is warm.</font>

466
00:33:12,109 --> 00:33:13,827
<font color="yellow">Yeah, it's totally warm.</font>

467
00:33:15,132 --> 00:33:16,132
<font color="yellow">Is that so?</font>

468
00:33:16,601 --> 00:33:17,601
<font color="yellow">Mom, here.</font>

469
00:33:18,216 --> 00:33:22,702
<font color="yellow">Is this toilet paper? You bought
exactly what we needed.</font>

470
00:33:23,124 --> 00:33:25,692
<font color="yellow">In South Korea, you buy
toilet paper for people who</font>

471
00:33:25,717 --> 00:33:28,433
<font color="yellow">just moved in so that things
will go smoothly for them.</font>

472
00:33:28,601 --> 00:33:32,686
<font color="yellow">Really? I think things are
going smoothly for me already.</font>

473
00:33:34,147 --> 00:33:35,147
<font color="yellow">Look.</font>

474
00:33:36,195 --> 00:33:38,062
<font color="yellow">Where did you get this ring?</font>

475
00:33:38,312 --> 00:33:42,749
<font color="yellow">I found it under the wardrobe
while I was moving out.</font>

476
00:33:43,124 --> 00:33:45,554
<font color="yellow">Didn't you lose this when you were mugged?</font>

477
00:33:45,999 --> 00:33:47,233
<font color="yellow">It's so strange.</font>

478
00:33:48,132 --> 00:33:50,399
<font color="yellow">I never took this ring off before.</font>

479
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:55,436
<font color="yellow">Oh, I was so happy after I found this ring!</font>

480
00:33:55,999 --> 00:33:59,288
<font color="yellow">Mom, I think things will go
smoothly for you from now on.</font>

481
00:34:00,007 --> 00:34:03,193
<font color="yellow">If I had known this would have happened,
I would've moved out a long time ago.</font>

482
00:34:03,218 --> 00:34:06,155
<font color="yellow">After moving here, I feel so relaxed.</font>

483
00:34:07,437 --> 00:34:10,314
<font color="yellow">This feels like a palace to me.</font>

484
00:34:11,554 --> 00:34:14,487
<font color="yellow">If you're relaxed and happy, I'm happy, too.</font>

485
00:34:15,046 --> 00:34:18,800
<font color="yellow">From now on, don't worry
about Yoo-sung and me, and</font>

486
00:34:19,028 --> 00:34:22,853
<font color="yellow">just live a happy life with
Jang-go and your in-laws.</font>

487
00:34:23,062 --> 00:34:25,445
<font color="yellow">I have no more wishes other than that.</font>

488
00:34:26,445 --> 00:34:27,684
<font color="yellow">All right.</font>

489
00:34:30,068 --> 00:34:32,411
<font color="yellow">But when are we going to eat pork feet?</font>

490
00:34:33,294 --> 00:34:34,294
<font color="yellow">How about now?</font>

491
00:34:37,153 --> 00:34:38,372
<font color="yellow">Mother, did you eat yet?</font>

492
00:34:39,060 --> 00:34:40,060
<font color="yellow">I'm hungry.</font>

493
00:34:41,786 --> 00:34:44,186
<font color="yellow">Are you serious? Mi-poong was fired?</font>

494
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:48,114
<font color="yellow">Yes, mother, so don't worry anymore.</font>

495
00:34:49,568 --> 00:34:52,301
<font color="yellow">But what if she's able to come back again?</font>

496
00:34:52,778 --> 00:34:56,640
<font color="yellow">That won't happen this time.
Grandfather fired her himself.</font>

497
00:34:57,177 --> 00:35:00,356
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness! How could this happen?</font>

498
00:35:00,918 --> 00:35:04,653
<font color="yellow">Oh my god! She deserves to be fired!</font>

499
00:35:05,176 --> 00:35:06,176
<font color="yellow">How could she-</font>

500
00:35:07,278 --> 00:35:09,340
<font color="yellow">How dare she hang up on me!</font>

501
00:35:10,505 --> 00:35:12,838
<font color="yellow">Oh, dear! I shouldn't be like this!</font>

502
00:35:14,677 --> 00:35:17,481
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil! Hwang Geum-sil!</font>

503
00:35:18,005 --> 00:35:20,405
<font color="yellow">What is she doing here at this hour?</font>

504
00:35:22,106 --> 00:35:23,589
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil!</font>

505
00:35:23,614 --> 00:35:26,525
<font color="yellow">What is it? Did your husband
cause trouble again?</font>

506
00:35:27,028 --> 00:35:29,501
<font color="yellow">My in-law doesn't live here anymore.
She moved out.</font>

507
00:35:30,021 --> 00:35:33,103
<font color="yellow">So I hope you won't
come here for her anymore.</font>

508
00:35:33,128 --> 00:35:34,816
<font color="yellow">That's not it.</font>

509
00:35:34,841 --> 00:35:35,908
<font color="yellow">Then what is it?</font>

510
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:40,075
<font color="yellow">Your daughter-in-law isn't
back from work yet, right?</font>

511
00:35:43,138 --> 00:35:45,871
<font color="yellow">Why do you care about my daughter-in-law?</font>

512
00:35:46,232 --> 00:35:48,637
<font color="yellow">Should I tell you this or not?</font>

513
00:35:48,903 --> 00:35:50,122
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

514
00:35:51,239 --> 00:35:54,130
<font color="yellow">Rummage through her bedroom.</font>

515
00:35:54,700 --> 00:35:55,981
<font color="yellow">You might find money in there!</font>

516
00:35:57,302 --> 00:35:59,667
<font color="yellow">What are you suddenly talking about?</font>

517
00:35:59,911 --> 00:36:01,444
<font color="yellow">What do you mean money?</font>

518
00:36:02,591 --> 00:36:04,450
<font color="yellow">You don't know anything.</font>

519
00:36:05,021 --> 00:36:08,477
<font color="yellow">Your daughter-in-law got caught for leaking</font>

520
00:36:08,502 --> 00:36:12,036
<font color="yellow">company information and getting money for it!</font>

521
00:36:12,061 --> 00:36:15,930
<font color="yellow">$300,000 came out from her desk!</font>

522
00:36:16,310 --> 00:36:17,497
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

523
00:36:17,755 --> 00:36:20,559
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong was fired.</font>

524
00:36:21,747 --> 00:36:23,051
<font color="yellow">What will you do, Geum-sil?</font>

525
00:36:24,083 --> 00:36:27,263
<font color="yellow">Is everything you said true?</font>

526
00:36:27,505 --> 00:36:30,813
<font color="yellow">Would I have come
all the way here if it wasn't?</font>

527
00:36:31,161 --> 00:36:35,590
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong made the company suffer
thousands of dollars in losses!</font>

528
00:36:35,857 --> 00:36:40,560
<font color="yellow">So she's supposed to go to prison right now,</font>

529
00:36:40,794 --> 00:36:45,012
<font color="yellow">but my daughter-in-law begged the
chairman not to go that far.</font>

530
00:36:45,849 --> 00:36:46,981
<font color="yellow">Prison?</font>

531
00:36:47,059 --> 00:36:50,950
<font color="yellow">If it wasn't for Shin-ae, Mi-poong
would be in big trouble by now!</font>

532
00:36:51,083 --> 00:36:54,552
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong was supposed to have paid
out of her pocket to pay for the damage.</font>

533
00:36:54,864 --> 00:36:58,873
<font color="yellow">If she couldn't do that, then your son
would've had to clean up the mess for her!</font>

534
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:04,130
<font color="yellow">Even if you had sold this house, you wouldn't
have been able to pay for everything.</font>

535
00:37:04,294 --> 00:37:05,778
<font color="yellow">My son...?</font>

536
00:37:06,388 --> 00:37:08,763
<font color="yellow">Oh my god! Geum-sil!</font>

537
00:37:08,788 --> 00:37:13,738
<font color="yellow">Oh! What's going on? Geum-sil, what happened?</font>

538
00:37:13,973 --> 00:37:18,497
<font color="yellow">- What's wrong with her?
- I didn't do anything.</font>

539
00:37:21,091 --> 00:37:23,433
<font color="yellow">- We're back.
- We're back.</font>

540
00:37:23,458 --> 00:37:26,258
<font color="yellow">Lee Jang-go, did you know about this, too?</font>

541
00:37:33,466 --> 00:37:34,949
<font color="yellow">What do you mean?</font>

542
00:37:35,950 --> 00:37:41,097
<font color="yellow">I heard Mi-poong received money
by leaking company information.</font>

543
00:37:41,434 --> 00:37:45,316
<font color="yellow">Money was found in your desk drawer.
Is that not true?</font>

544
00:37:46,558 --> 00:37:50,368
<font color="yellow">Jang-go, don't try to lie
and tell me the truth.</font>

545
00:37:51,043 --> 00:37:53,839
<font color="yellow">Is that true or not?</font>

546
00:37:54,801 --> 00:37:55,981
<font color="yellow">Mom, the thing is...</font>

547
00:37:57,082 --> 00:37:59,097
<font color="yellow">it's true that money was found, but...</font>

548
00:38:01,543 --> 00:38:03,589
<font color="yellow">It's true. It's true!</font>

549
00:38:03,614 --> 00:38:04,614
<font color="yellow">- Mom!
- Mother!</font>

550
00:38:04,793 --> 00:38:05,793
<font color="yellow">Move!</font>

551
00:38:07,293 --> 00:38:08,493
<font color="yellow">I had my doubts...</font>

552
00:38:09,246 --> 00:38:10,929
<font color="yellow">I didn't think this was true.</font>

553
00:38:11,285 --> 00:38:13,960
<font color="yellow">But you're saying that
everything I heard is true!</font>

554
00:38:14,206 --> 00:38:16,285
<font color="yellow">Mom, calm down and listen to me.</font>

555
00:38:16,310 --> 00:38:18,345
<font color="yellow">Calm down? Listen to you?</font>

556
00:38:19,605 --> 00:38:21,855
<font color="yellow">Mother, what do we do?</font>

557
00:38:22,473 --> 00:38:25,048
<font color="yellow">Nam-yi, what do we do about Jang-go now?</font>

558
00:38:27,152 --> 00:38:29,028
<font color="yellow">Tell me! Why did you do that?</font>

559
00:38:29,371 --> 00:38:31,188
<font color="yellow">Who are you trying to ruin?</font>

560
00:38:31,465 --> 00:38:34,416
<font color="yellow">Were you going to give that
money to Jang-go or me?</font>

561
00:38:34,832 --> 00:38:36,535
<font color="yellow">Why on earth would you do such a thing?</font>

562
00:38:36,824 --> 00:38:39,074
<font color="yellow">What the heck did you do
when you were in North Korea?</font>

563
00:38:39,637 --> 00:38:43,487
<font color="yellow">You put on an innocent front.
How can you steal?</font>

564
00:38:43,512 --> 00:38:46,261
<font color="yellow">Mother, it's not me. I really didn't do this!</font>

565
00:38:46,598 --> 00:38:50,512
<font color="yellow">I don't know why this happened
to me, but please believe me!</font>

566
00:38:51,066 --> 00:38:54,706
<font color="yellow">Money was found in your drawer!
But you still don't know about this?</font>

567
00:38:56,121 --> 00:38:58,324
<font color="yellow">You and your mom are the same!</font>

568
00:38:58,973 --> 00:39:01,446
<font color="yellow">Like mother, like daughter.
Both of you commit all</font>

569
00:39:01,471 --> 00:39:03,992
<font color="yellow">the wrongdoings and yet
you declare you're innocent.</font>

570
00:39:04,309 --> 00:39:05,309
<font color="yellow">Mom!</font>

571
00:39:05,334 --> 00:39:07,804
<font color="yellow">Oh, now I see! You were going to
give that money to your mom,</font>

572
00:39:07,829 --> 00:39:10,082
<font color="yellow">weren't you? Were you
going to buy her a house?</font>

573
00:39:10,668 --> 00:39:13,002
<font color="yellow">No. I really didn't do it.</font>

574
00:39:13,027 --> 00:39:16,482
<font color="yellow">No need to talk this out. Pack your things
and get out of my house.</font>

575
00:39:16,691 --> 00:39:23,013
<font color="yellow">I don't want to talk with you, so get out!</font>

576
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:27,496
<font color="yellow">- Mom!
- Get a hold of yourself, Geum-sil!</font>

577
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:35,531
<font color="yellow">Mother, I can put up with everything
else but a daughter-in-law like her.</font>

578
00:39:36,473 --> 00:39:40,531
<font color="yellow">She's a thief! A con-artist!</font>

579
00:39:41,121 --> 00:39:45,551
<font color="yellow">Mother, no matter how poor
I was, I never stole anything!</font>

580
00:39:46,184 --> 00:39:49,536
<font color="yellow">Even if I got extra change,
I couldn't sleep from the guilt</font>

581
00:39:49,561 --> 00:39:52,689
<font color="yellow">and had to go give it back in
order to fall asleep well!</font>

582
00:39:53,090 --> 00:39:56,347
<font color="yellow">Yet, you want me to live with
a daughter-in-law like her?</font>

583
00:39:56,707 --> 00:39:59,683
<font color="yellow">Mother, I can't do that even if I die!</font>

584
00:40:00,051 --> 00:40:03,949
<font color="yellow">Oh my goodness. What will we do?</font>

585
00:40:05,495 --> 00:40:09,096
<font color="yellow">- Why are you just standing there? Get out!
- Mom!</font>

586
00:40:09,605 --> 00:40:10,605
<font color="yellow">Get out!</font>

587
00:40:12,801 --> 00:40:14,423
<font color="yellow">- Mi-poong!
- Where are you going?</font>

588
00:40:14,754 --> 00:40:16,621
<font color="yellow">What are you going to do with that thief?</font>

589
00:40:16,809 --> 00:40:19,680
<font color="yellow">Mom! Mi-poong said it wasn't true!</font>

590
00:40:20,332 --> 00:40:21,931
<font color="yellow">How can you only trust someone else?</font>

591
00:40:23,488 --> 00:40:24,722
<font color="yellow">You're too much.</font>

592
00:40:25,277 --> 00:40:29,660
<font color="yellow">Fine! You leave, too!
Leave and never come back again!</font>

593
00:40:29,685 --> 00:40:32,456
<font color="yellow">All of you leave! All of you!</font>

594
00:40:33,667 --> 00:40:37,847
<font color="yellow">- I must have lived for too long.
- Mom, what's wrong with you?</font>

595
00:40:38,129 --> 00:40:40,605
<font color="yellow">- What do I do?
- Mom, get a hold of yourself!</font>

596
00:40:42,207 --> 00:40:43,207
<font color="yellow">Grandma...</font>

597
00:40:44,339 --> 00:40:45,339
<font color="yellow">Massage her.</font>

