00:58:11,676 --> 00:58:13,276
<font color="yellow">Don't even call my name!</font>

796
00:58:13,402 --> 00:58:15,320
<font color="yellow">I'm done with you.</font>

797
00:58:16,934 --> 00:58:17,934
<font color="yellow">Ms. Hwang.</font>

798
00:58:21,832 --> 00:58:25,198
<font color="yellow">Please think about our kids.</font>

799
00:58:25,596 --> 00:58:28,550
<font color="yellow">They've living nicely together.
This is wrong.</font>

800
00:58:29,168 --> 00:58:30,542
<font color="yellow">They'll get hurt.</font>

801
00:58:31,480 --> 00:58:32,480
<font color="yellow">Ms. Hwang,</font>

802
00:58:33,723 --> 00:58:36,370
<font color="yellow">if I'm the problem, I'll cut off my ties with</font>

803
00:58:36,394 --> 00:58:38,810
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong, just as I promised to last time.</font>

804
00:58:39,113 --> 00:58:42,433
<font color="yellow">I won't look at her. I won't meet her.
I'll cut off all ties with her.</font>

805
00:58:42,458 --> 00:58:46,215
<font color="yellow">So please let her live with Jang-go.</font>

806
00:58:46,660 --> 00:58:49,732
<font color="yellow">Please love her as your daughter-in-law.</font>

807
00:58:49,989 --> 00:58:52,886
<font color="yellow">That's all I want, Ms. Hwang.</font>

808
00:58:54,144 --> 00:59:00,369
<font color="yellow">I'm begging you, Ms. Hwang. So please...</font>

809
00:59:00,777 --> 00:59:05,401
<font color="yellow">Take these and go! Just go!</font>

810
00:59:05,793 --> 00:59:09,963
<font color="yellow">Why are both of you being so stubborn?</font>

811
00:59:09,988 --> 00:59:12,488
<font color="yellow">- I told you to leave!
- Ms. Hwang.</font>

812
00:59:18,004 --> 00:59:19,569
<font color="yellow">I'm glad you're here.</font>

813
00:59:19,889 --> 00:59:22,436
<font color="yellow">Take your belongings
and leave with your mother.</font>

814
00:59:22,683 --> 00:59:24,761
<font color="yellow">Please just go!</font>

815
00:59:27,176 --> 00:59:28,176
<font color="yellow">Mom.</font>

816
00:59:36,012 --> 00:59:38,136
<font color="yellow">- Mom, let's go.
- Mi-poong...</font>

817
00:59:39,965 --> 00:59:41,462
<font color="yellow">I can't do this any longer.</font>

818
00:59:45,137 --> 00:59:47,804
<font color="yellow">- No, Mi-poong. You can't do this!
- No!</font>

819
00:59:48,113 --> 00:59:49,246
<font color="yellow">I've done enough.</font>

820
00:59:50,160 --> 00:59:55,013
<font color="yellow">We didn't suffer through all
those troubles to live like this.</font>

821
00:59:57,769 --> 01:00:01,308
<font color="yellow">Father wouldn't want me to live like this.</font>

822
01:00:01,699 --> 01:00:02,699
<font color="yellow">So let's go.</font>

823
01:00:04,379 --> 01:00:06,635
<font color="yellow">Good-bye, mother.</font>

824
01:00:07,337 --> 01:00:08,667
<font color="yellow">Good-bye, Aunt Nam-yi.</font>

825
01:00:09,410 --> 01:00:13,058
<font color="yellow">Please tell grandmother that I'm sorry.</font>

826
01:00:20,957 --> 01:00:23,168
<font color="yellow">- Let's go!
- Mi-poong!</font>

827
01:00:24,551 --> 01:00:25,551
<font color="yellow">Let's go.</font>

828
01:00:34,840 --> 01:00:37,074
<font color="yellow">Geum-sil! My goodness!</font>

829
01:00:56,519 --> 01:00:59,328
<font color="yellow">- Let's talk.
- Let's go.</font>

830
01:01:26,348 --> 01:01:30,319
<font color="yellow">Mi-poong left home. It's late, but
you should learn to move on now.</font>

831
01:01:31,074 --> 01:01:32,141
<font color="yellow">Mom, you really-!</font>

832
01:01:34,168 --> 01:01:36,597
<font color="yellow">If you want to go after her, go ahead.</font>

833
01:01:37,347 --> 01:01:41,214
<font color="yellow">However, I can't accept her as
my daughter-in-law anymore.</font>

834
01:01:43,683 --> 01:01:44,683
<font color="yellow">Fine.</font>

835
01:01:45,691 --> 01:01:46,758
<font color="yellow">I'll leave, too.</font>

836
01:02:09,527 --> 01:02:12,581
<font color="yellow">Hi, Mi-poong. Where are you right now?</font>

837
01:02:24,816 --> 01:02:25,816
<font color="yellow">Jang-go.</font>

838
01:02:28,043 --> 01:02:29,671
<font color="yellow">I have a favor to ask of you.</font>

839
01:02:31,262 --> 01:02:32,729
<font color="yellow">You must do it for me.</font>

840
01:02:37,832 --> 01:02:38,832
<font color="yellow">What is it?</font>

841
01:02:44,068 --> 01:02:47,990
<font color="yellow">Let's... get a divorce.</font>

842
01:02:51,162 --> 01:02:52,162
<font color="yellow">What?</font>

843
01:03:00,160 --> 01:03:05,565
<font color="yellow"><i>The wind, the sunlight, the memories</i></font>

844
01:03:05,565 --> 01:03:13,273
<font color="yellow"><i>I can't forget the beautiful days</i></font>

845
01:03:13,427 --> 01:03:14,933
<font color="yellow">(Blow Breeze)</font>

846
01:03:15,177 --> 01:03:18,747
<font color="yellow">I hate you. I hate everyone.
I hate even looking at you now!</font>

847
01:03:18,943 --> 01:03:21,484
<font color="yellow">Mom, don't send me back there.
Don't tell me to go.</font>

848
01:03:21,787 --> 01:03:24,342
<font color="yellow">You don't have to go.
The three of us can live together.</font>

849
01:03:24,367 --> 01:03:25,792
<font color="yellow">What are you doing?</font>

850
01:03:25,818 --> 01:03:28,741
<font color="yellow">You just have to say one
warm word of apology to her.</font>

851
01:03:30,443 --> 01:03:31,443
<font color="yellow">Make red bean noodles.</font>

852
01:03:31,771 --> 01:03:33,280
<font color="yellow">- Red bean noodles?
- Yes.</font>

853
01:03:33,513 --> 01:03:35,638
<font color="yellow">I can't digest it. Make pumpkin porridge.</font>

854
01:03:35,771 --> 01:03:38,372
<font color="yellow">- Yes!
- I'll go!</font>

855
01:03:38,701 --> 01:03:40,691
<font color="yellow">Use your words!</font>

856
01:03:40,716 --> 01:03:43,548
<font color="yellow">- You're going to own this one day.
- Me?</font>

857
01:03:43,573 --> 01:03:44,573
<font color="yellow">It's been a long time.</font>

858
01:03:44,598 --> 01:03:46,265
<font color="yellow">Have you found my father?</font>

859
01:03:46,966 --> 01:03:47,966
<font color="yellow">Your father?</font>

